

Event

- type flags
  #set of flags to classify event
- rarity
  #Rarity scale of event
- Set of roles
  - name
  - assigned player (None)
  - is optional
- Start operator
  # starts event (might move people to new location)
- End operator
  # ends event


Character

 - Interests
  # type flags map to value
  # used to give events preference
 - goal set
  - each operator takes population and return value


Event Operator
 - takes set of roles with people assigned

Type flag
 - Types of events / interests (outdoor, active, ...)

Goal operator
 - Looks as full population and produces scalar value for goal

Events are selected based on interest match to character, event rarity, and their
alignment with player goal
